name: Invesco Fundamental High Yield Corporate Bond Index ETF
longDescription: QQC seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the NASDAQ -100 Index, or any successor thereto, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units. Invesco Fundamental High Yield Corporate Bond Index ETF (the ETF) seeks to replicate, before fees and expenses, the performance of its underlying index, the RAFI Bonds US High Yield 1-10 Index, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units.
